#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1245
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:1513
msgid ""
"This algorithm drops existing primary keys or FID values and regenerates "
"them in output layers."
msgstr ""
"Den här algoritmen tar bort befintliga primärnycklar eller FID-värden och "
"återskapar dem i utdatalagren."

