"If checked, naturally sorts the features based on the provided expression "
"(i.e., 'a9' < 'a10')."
msgstr ""
"Om markerad sorteras funktionerna naturligt utifrån det angivna uttrycket "
"(t.ex. 'a9' < 'a10')."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:951
msgid "**Path group expression**"
msgstr "**Stiggruppsuttryck**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorcreation.rst:954
