"For each feature (polygon / multi-polygon) geometry in the input layer, the "
"given number of points is added to the result layer."
msgstr ""
"För varje geometri (polygon/multipolygon) i inmatningslagret läggs det "
"angivna antalet punkter till i resultatlagret."

